{
  "info": {
    "name": "Telephony Webhook API",
    "description": "Test collection for the telephony vendor webhook endpoint (POST /api/calls/inbound) and read endpoints (GET /api/calls/telephony, GET /api/calls/telephony/stats).\n\n## Important: Intercom-based Call Routing\n\nThe `intercom_number` field is **critical** for proper call routing. When provided, the incoming call popup and socket events are delivered ONLY to the agent assigned to that intercom number.\n\n- If your vendor sends `intercom_number: \"1002\"`, only Agent B (assigned intercom 1002) gets the popup.\n- If omitted, all users with `calls:receive_sip_events` permission receive the event (fallback).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000"
    },
    {
      "key": "webhookSecret",
      "value": "a3f8c1e9d4b7a2f6c9e8b1d5f7a3c6e9b2d4f8a1c5e7b9d3f6a8c1e9f2a59f2a5"
    },
    {
      "key": "authToken",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{authToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Login (get token)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"admin@medilead.com\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin@123\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
        }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.token) {",
              "  pm.collectionVariables.set('authToken', jsonData.data.token);",
              "  console.log('Token saved:', jsonData.data.token.substring(0, 20) + '...');",
              "}"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Health Check",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "health"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "Webhook - Completed Call (inbound) - Intercom 1001",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"caller_phone_number\": \"+919876543210\",\n  \"call_status\": \"completed\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-24T10:45:00Z\",\n  \"duration_seconds\": 142,\n  \"vendor_call_id\": \"vc_test_001\",\n  \"direction\": \"inbound\",\n  \"intercom_number\": \"1001\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/calls/inbound",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "calls", "inbound"]
        }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "var body = pm.request.body.raw;",
              "var secret = pm.collectionVariables.get('webhookSecret');",
              "var sig = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(body, secret).toString();",
              "pm.request.headers.add({ key: 'X-Webhook-Signature', value: sig });",
              "console.log('Signature:', sig);"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
